author: rhuijben
msg: Properly skip obstructing working copies when adding files and directories
(svn_wc_notify_action_t): Rename value to better describe its usage.
add_file): An addition that has status normal must be an obstructing
working copy, so directly skip it to make sure we don't change anything
inside. Remove old detection code. Simplify tree conflict constraints.
(forced_checkout_with_versioned_obstruction): Expect a skip instead of an
(forced_switch_failures): Expect skip instead of an error and update
(forced_update_failures): Expect skip instead of an error.
